Name: Miyoshi muscular dystrophy 1
Definition: A Miyoshi muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in mutation in the DYSF gene on chromosome 2p13.

Name: Miyoshi muscular dystrophy 2
Definition: A Miyoshi muscular dystrophy characterized by asymmetric presentation of muscle weakness and atrophy that has_material_basis_in a locus on chromosome 10.

Name: Miyoshi muscular dystrophy 3
Definition: A Miyoshi muscular dystrophy that has_material_basis_in mutation in the ANO5 gene on chromosome 11p14.
